[04:13.21]	from all: the rest
[04:14.70]	Shall bear the business in some other fight,
[04:17.80]	As cause will be obey'd. Please you to march;
[04:20.90]	And four shall quickly draw out my command,
[04:23.94]	Which men are best inclined.
[04:26.05]COMINIUS	March on, my fellows:
[04:27.66]	Make good this ostentation, and you shall
